::KitKat::

She went along the scent trail.  She picked up strongly on this male wolf's 
scent. "He was here recently." she said.  She went along untill she got a 
glimps of another wolf.  She ducted behind a tree.  His scent was strong to 
her now.  She smelled Maximal from him. She crouched down at the base of the 
tree,looking at him.  She kept under the shrubs and bushes to stay out of 
sight.  She only watched and would report her findings to her new pack 
leader, Megatron.
